    <item>
      <title>鲍曼敦促美联储“谨慎”进一步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-20/bowman-urges-fed-to-proceed-cautiously-on-further-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事米歇尔·鲍曼表示：“我更愿意谨慎地降低政策利率，以便更好地评估我们距离终点还有多远”，因为降低通胀的进展已经放缓。鲍曼周三在佛罗里达州西棕榈滩的棕榈滩论坛俱乐部发表了讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-20/bowman-urges-fed-to-proceed-cautiously-on-further-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 18:09:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
